{"title":"国庆颂","authors":["李济深"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李济深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开国九周年国庆节，欣睹社会主义大跃进中辉煌奇迹，喜赋七绝二十四章为颂，借与六亿同胞共申欢欣鼓舞之忱云尔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年开国庆今朝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众欢腾震碧寥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数英雄艰缔造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰碑灿烂矗云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无私援助仗苏联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子成堆核热传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酷爱和平非怕战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更教讹诈化云烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两大宣言十月节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风经已压西风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨人隔岁重相聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结中苏水乳融。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"援朝猛士唱刀环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉相连义重山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生力归来参建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇勋应不让兵间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫净乌云见碧空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条道路斗争中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白旗拔尽红旗立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整改宏收不世功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破除迷信茁多才，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放思维智慧开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动万端齐跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都从总路线中来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整风倡导行全国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展工农奇迹多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂帅自然推政治，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢思敢做是先河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?梓楩楠适土宜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千红万紫显多姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山原绿遍风沙少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜离离果熟时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土洋结合际风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科技同时大进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界创新凭手脑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停革命策奇勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经天纬地八方开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各辟新程向九垓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷气直升车电化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日边飞去日边来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移山毅力赛愚公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造海翻成水利通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月胜于千载绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疏河夏禹漫论功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电子潜通计算机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秘搜半导体非奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新电视供周览，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莺弄歌喉蝶舞衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车自造事平平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银翼横空更制成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航海巨轮排浪出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风万里慑长鲸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运河北道通南道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预计功成伟绝伦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸垂杨青不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳门接候潮门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁不分洋土炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉处处映天红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业争能公社办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城乡无别化工农。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢粮机械三元帅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交通电力两先行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一日等于二十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎头赶美定超英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农具翻新花样鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轴承个个滚珠圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电犁电镐同时进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一日能耕万顷田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦翻绿浪稻翻云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亩产十三万几斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘使米丘林复起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也教心折此奇闻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社大家庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结合工农商学兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会日臻高度化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萌芽共产肇先声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体全民逐步趋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提高速度向康衢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马恩理想非遥远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各尽所能取所需。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保粮防病策非虚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国迅将四害除，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处红旗都插遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年丰人寿乐何如。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云涌风从势莫京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矫然崛起是民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄师昭示新威力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捍卫和平反战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫诧今年胜往昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年定更胜今年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌奇迹何由致？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举国讴歌领导贤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万般成就数难清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盈耳洋洋歌颂声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处民安兼物阜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普天同庆乐承平。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}